features: «PRODUCT INCLUDES - 1 PCS folding design 10 compartment pill case box (Translucent Blue) + 297 PCS medication brand labels + 28 PCS white labels. The pill box is made of food grade healthy material, safe and odorless for storing medications. Size: 3.7 "Lx2.5 "Wx1.18 "H, basically equivalent to a credit card size. A good personal or family, work, outing or travel essentials medication organizer container.

«BULK 297 PRE-CUT BRAND LABELS - these labels are pre-cut. The labels' size match the the inner lids' size perfectly , just peel off them and stick on the corresponding lids. 297 labels are printed in high definition and with no duplicates. Contains most of the household medications, such as regular medicines, vitamins, cod liver oil, supplements and more.

«28 SMALL WHITE LABELS - In addition to the brand labels, these white labels can be used alone or with brand labels. You can stick them on the outside of the inner lid and write the name of the medication or reminders (such as 2 times a day, 3 times a day, 1 tablet a time, etc.). You can also stick it on the inside of the inner lid to mark the dosage or other reminders.

«FOLDING DESIGN, EASY TO CARRY - Folding design mini pharmacy are small, handy, portable and space saving. You can easily put them in small bags or pockets, drawers, car storage compartments, and even some purses. Secure double-lock design protects your medication cleanly and safely, prevents pills from falling out or getting dusty during daily use. The inner cover can be removed as a single unit for filling pills or cleaning.

«FIT MULTIPLE MEDICATIONS STORAGE - These 10-compartment cute pill holder dispenser boxes are perfect for holding a variety of medications, whether you take them daily or weekly. Each pill holder box has 10 compartments, 4 large and 6 small compartments to accommodate different sizes and quantities of medications. Suitable for most common medications such as vitamins, cod liver oil, supplements and other medications.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great organizer depending on your intended use
reviews.reviewText: I bought this pill organizer recently as a way to take a variety of medications with me out and about while on a vacation. Overall, I'm happy with this product. But depending on intended use, there might be better options.How I used this organizer: I used each compartment to contain a different medication so that I could have a variety of potential needs at my fingertips--Tylenol, Ibuprofen, Antacids, and some of my needed daily medications. I then taped the medication label to each of the organizer tabs so I could identify what it contained. This organizer worked well for this purpose to have a significant supply of my smaller pills and a couple of doses of larger pills. Basically, it could get me through a couple days of being in motion and away from my hotel room without restocking.What this organizer won't be good for: I typically take a lot of vitamins that are on the larger side. I simply couldn't fit these and left behind for this trip. Another example is a standard tums--I could only fit 2 tums in the compartments I had available, so I committed a couple of compartments to Tums. If you are someone that has pills on the larger size, this just isn't going to work well for you. Admittedly, I haven't found a good compact option when large pills are needed.Overall, very helpful to have an emergency stash while out and about on vacation, and a high quality compartment that seems like it will hold up to daily use.
